data.description: This 2 Bedroom townhome is located on the south side in a gated community! This home has a spacious living room, wood burning fireplace, and fully remodeled kitchen with a breakfast bar. Bathroom has double sinks and vanity area, and both bedrooms have walk-in closets. Stainless steel appliances and washer and dryer are included. Attached 2 car garage contains plenty of space for storage. Remote entry into gate and garage. Community swimming pool. Yard upkeep is included, so you never have to worry about mowing the grass! Pets are welcome.
